            "title": "Serological Survey of Lyssaviruses in Polish Bats in the Frame of Passive Rabies Surveillance Using an Enzyme-Linked Immunosorbent Assay",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Anna",
                    "lastName": "Orłowska"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Marcin",
